Exercise 4
----------

In this exercise you are to do something similar to the last one.
Go ahead and hook 4 four LEDs to the pi, and one button.  When
the button is pressed either the lights 1 and 3 should illuminate
or lights 2 and 4 should illuminate.  When pressed again the pair of
lights that are lit should alternate.

--------
Hints
--------

1)  Use VARIABLES FOR YOUR PIN NUMBERS!!  You will get lost if you
    do not use this.

2)  Refer to previous exercies for this one, nothing is added but
    complexity.
